description: Number of non-Abelian groups of order n.
comments: a(n) = 0 iff n belongs to sequence A051532.
links: T. D. Noe, Table of n, a(n) for n=1..2015
Index entries for sequences related to groups
example: a(6) = 1 because the only non-Abelian group of order 6 is the symmetric group S_3.
author: Ahmed Fares (ahmedfares(AT)my-deja.com), Apr 19 2001
